hits.longDescription:
• 3 pairs of cucumber-rose infused under-eye patches.
  • Paraben-Free. Sulfate-Free. Formaldehyde-Free. Silicone-Free.
  • Apply day or night.
  • Tear open sachet. Remove each eye mask. Apply one sheet under each eye area. Let sit for 15-20 minutes. Dispose of the masks and use your ring finger to massage excess formulation around the eye area. Let fully absorb and follow up with your normal skincare routine.
  • Full Ingredients
  • Please note: This item cannot ship to Hawaii, Puerto Rico, or Canada.

  • Ingredients: Water, Glycerin, Polysorbate 20, Xanthan Gum, Phenoxyethanol, Hydrolyzed Jojoba Esters, Sodium PCA, Caprylyl Glycol, Fragrance, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Flower Extract, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Extract, Althaea Officinalis Root Extract, Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Extract, Rosa Damascena Flower Oil, Panthenol, Ascorbyl Glucoside, Citric Acid.
     
  • Style No. C5074
hits.shortDescription: This limited-edition collaboration pairs our playful, free-spirited attitude with the beauty mastery of Sephora Collection. Inspired by the eternally fresh beauty of our iconic Tea Roses, this eye mask set includes 3 pairs of aloe, chamomile and cucumber extract-infused patches that help soothe, depuff and hydrate the undereye area. Formulated for all skin types, the curved sheets contour to your skin to reduce dryness, dullness, uneven texture and dark circles.
